{"tid":2411430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Angelababy用英文名被內地作家鬧爆 陶傑出手諗中文名俾網民投票","createTime":"2021-02-17T10:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T20:46:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":207,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"4e6f2bb9b22c431a8396f949b429f86f83765104","tid":2411430,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NaMy.FNUXJqHdYU9kGwCtQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUyMi44OTM2MTcwMjEyNzY2/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-02/cde97990-70f9-11eb-beff-3b6fc013c1b2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNaMy.FNUXJqHdYU9kGwCtQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUyMi44OTM2MTcwMjEyNzY2%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-02%2Fcde97990-70f9-11eb-beff-3b6fc013c1b2&h=e6c49239&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國「知名作家」劉信達經常喺微博發表偉論，過往有唔少藝人「躺著也中槍」，包括謝霆鋒、王菲、陳小春、王寶強及楊冪等等。劉信達試過警告謝霆鋒喺3個月內必須要搞清楚同王菲嘅關係，一係就結婚、一係就分手。最新就輪到近年喺內地發展不俗嘅Angelababy（楊穎）, 劉信達喺微博鬧爆Baby身為中國人，偏偏用英文名, 「西方人對應的是東方人，而不是南方人，不要無知者無畏，不要無聊當有趣！」佢又話內地人對外國節日及洋化覺得反感，希望Baby對自己個英文名反感，建議佢用返中文名喺內地發展。<br />\n<br />\n香港才子陶傑睇到都忍唔住出手幫Baby講返兩句，陶傑指Baby用英文名唔係因為祟洋，而係想鼓勵下一代學好英文，好似Maggie Q同Lisa S都有中國或亞裔血統，廣電局都無要求佢哋用中文名。而且「Angelababy」發音簡單，小學程度也叫得出口，可以證明「英文不是障礙」。另外，陶傑仲幫Baby諗咗幾個中文名俾大家投票，包括「安琪拉嬰兒」、「安琪拉貝比」同埋「安琪拉悲B」，唔知Baby鍾意邊個名多啲呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FdJYidAAe810kijkIXmPRA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-02/fa7a9530-70f8-11eb-bf57-a0efefe170bd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFdJYidAAe810kijkIXmPRA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-02%2Ffa7a9530-70f8-11eb-bf57-a0efefe170bd&h=3f8c36d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b17063dbe85cabc799ee931ec2c4ce2d8ccf1a2","tid":2411430,"uid":343712,"like":78,"dislike":3,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:28:50.000Z","msg":"觀陰悲乙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d6a4247d89d835e052490e40d67ce727356144","tid":2411430,"uid":2267,"like":156,"dislike":0,"score":156,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:29:21.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">包括「安琪拉嬰兒」、「安琪拉貝比」同埋「安琪拉悲B」</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056a877bc08ae55fd14e1e1c3c1f1277cbfe09e9","tid":2411430,"uid":266342,"like":453,"dislike":3,"score":450,"citedBy":16,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:29:56.000Z","msg":"愛支那 巨嬰<br />\n<br />\n同原名幾貼切"},{"pid":"ae72d9fb4906b1ce1de9180d600a64e006216552","tid":2411430,"uid":22553,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:30:34.000Z","msg":"支語併音咪又係英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e02fcd25c2b94243f77b38f353d68b432cce64","tid":2411430,"uid":121546,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"ae72d9fb4906b1ce1de9180d600a64e006216552","tid":2411430,"uid":22553,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:30:34.000Z","msg":"支語併音咪又係英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:32:32.000Z","msg":"應該學韓國同台灣咁自創一套拼音文字啦"},{"pid":"eea936e8092ff0c3081dcbc91a14b945786d0f07","tid":2411430,"uid":56807,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:33:23.000Z","msg":"悲 B係咪解悲慘嘅西"},{"pid":"117cfc46ed81c2ae3df82d921fa18f80349b8d81","tid":2411430,"uid":15815,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:33:42.000Z","msg":"安逼兒(捲脷)"},{"pid":"ac0601b25243749d0df4e12da94aa5a2d9d2fcba","tid":2411430,"uid":137569,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:33:42.000Z","msg":"神仙啤/神仙b<img src=\"/assets/